org.beryx.streamplify.permutation

Class Permutations

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.beryx.streamplify.StreamableProxy<int[],Permutations>
      • org.beryx.streamplify.permutation.Permutations
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Streamable<int[],Permutations>

    public class Permutations
extends StreamableProxy<int[],Permutations>
    A Streamable providing streams of permutations.
    This class is a proxy that delegates to either LongPermutations or BigIntegerPermutations, depending on the permutation length.
